## Disclaimer

This software is a **research prototype** and **proof of concept** only.

**NOT INTENDED FOR CLINICAL USE.** Smart NOA has not been validated in clinical 
settings, has not received regulatory approval from the FDA or any other medical 
device authority, and should not be used to make clinical decisions or control 
actual medical devices.

Any clinical implementation would require:
- Extensive validation and verification testing
- Regulatory approval (FDA, CE Mark, etc.)
- Integration with certified medical device hardware
- Prospective clinical trials
- Institutional review board (IRB) approval

The authors assume no liability for any use of this software in clinical settings.
